      • addSetOrGetPrefix

        public static java.lang.String addSetOrGetPrefix(java.lang.String propertyName,
                                                 boolean isSet)
                                          throws ReflectionException
        Setter or getter method for parameter name generation

        name, true will return setName name, false will reutrn getName

        参数:
        propertyName - param's name
        isSet - is it create 'set' method,if not will be 'get'
        返回:
        the setter of getter method's name from param's name
        抛出:
        ReflectionException - Data format Exception
        从以下版本开始:
        1.0

      • getFieldList

        public static java.util.List<java.lang.String> getFieldList(java.lang.Object o,
                                                            int superClassDeep,
                                                            FieldNameFilter fieldNameFilter,
                                                            boolean canRepeat)
        get properties' name from one class
        参数:
        o - be extracted class
        superClassDeep - The deep of the extracting (start 0, less than 0 returns empty, 1 looks up for a class (this class + direct parent class). 2. Look up for two parent classes (this class + direct parent + direct parent). One-time analogy; - 2: All parent classes)
        fieldNameFilter - Field name filter
        canRepeat - is can be repeat
        返回:
        file's name list
        从以下版本开始:
        1.0
        另请参阅:
        FieldNameFilter
